5 Subject: Education; Agency of Education duties
6 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to require the
7 Secretary of Education to (1) provide statewide technical assistance to school
8 districts and supervisory unions on the implementation of all statewide
9 requirements and (2) conduct a comprehensive program evaluation and
10 organizational analysis of the Agency of Education and report back to the
11 House and Senate Committees on Education with recommendations for
12 changes to the Agency of Education.
13 An act relating to the role and structure of the Agency of Education
14 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
