6 Sec. 2. AGENCY OF EDUCATION PROGRAM EVALUATION AND
7 ORGANIZATIONAL ANALYSIS; REPORT
8 (a) The Secretary of Education shall conduct a comprehensive program
9 evaluation and organizational analysis of the Agency of Education, which shall
10 include:
11 (1) an evaluation of the culture of the Agency;
12 (2) an Agency-wide pay scale analysis;
13 (3) an inventory of the training and reporting requirements currently
14 required of school districts by the Agency and the origin of those requirements;
15 and
16 (4) any other component of the Agency the Secretary deems relevant.
17 (b) On or before January 15, 2026, the Secretary shall issue a written report
18 to the Senate and House Committees on Education with the findings of the
19 evaluation and analysis required under subsection (a) of this section. The
20 report shall include the Secretary’s recommendations for any changes to the
21 Agency, efforts already underway to complete such changes, a timeline for any
